title: Bartered Gold - Religion Of His Realm
description:
Bartered Gold is an expirimental electronic duo, with the debut album Religion Of His Realm created by only one member of the two. Their focus is to make music that does not sound like the same recycled boring electronic music that currently is being pumped out by mainstream producers.

This album consists of the slower, ambient-types of music with some chiptunes and drum and bass thrown in. The album can be purchased (Or downloaded in other formats) at
